      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 29.11 - 老子 29.13</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 29.9 - 老子 29.10</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>是以聖人去甚，去奢，去泰。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The store in ruins mocks our toil. Hence the sage puts away excessive effort, extravagance, and easy indulgence.</seg>
      </tuv>
